title: Medication-Graph-FHIR-Converter
message: >-
  This is the specific version of the repository of the 2026
  paper "Mapping MMI Pharmindex Items to RxNorm Semantic
  Clinical Drugs - An Evaluation Study"
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Markus
    family-names: Budeus
    email: markus.budeus@tum.de
