repository-code: >-
  https://github.com/medizininformatik-initiative/Medication-Graph-FHIR-Converter/tree/paper-2026-rxnorm-matching
abstract: >-
  This application loads the MMI Pharmindex files into a
  Neo4j knowledge graph and exports them as FHIR resources
  compliant with the MMI Core Data Set.

  This specific version is modified to enable matching drugs
  in the knowledge graph to RxNorm Semantic Clinical Drugs
  and to validate the generated matches using RxNorm-ATC
  mappings from Athena.
